                p.team-bio A00016965

        section.mission-block(style="margin-top: 80px;")
            h2 Our Commitment to Safety & Ethics
            p Dracarys was designed with child safeguarding at its core. All tutors are verified with university email addresses. Parents have full visibility over all messaging between tutors and their children.
            p We comply fully with GDPR — collecting only the minimum data required. Our platform includes a content flagging system, moderation controls, and a clear code of conduct for all tutors.

        section.cta-section(style="border-radius: 24px; margin-bottom: 80px;")
            .cta-inner
                h2 Ready to Join the Community?
                p Whether you're a parent looking for a tutor, or a university student wanting to give back — Dracarys is for you.
                .hero-buttons(style="justify-content: center;")
                    a.hero-btn.primary(href="/signup") Get Started Today
                    a.hero-btn.outline(href="/login") Already have an account? Sign in